{"tid":1974744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小六絲打寫文宣：時代揀中我哋","createTime":"2020-04-16T05:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T07:05:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"39da2c1922da97634bd1dbb95d10a79a0aea57f0","tid":1974744,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200416/35D5U45IP4MJ62X7KCY26N4JDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2F35D5U45IP4MJ62X7KCY26N4JDY%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=b3fc162e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2F35D5U45IP4MJ62X7KCY26N4JDY%2F&h=7c251ef7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200416/35D5U45IP4MJ62X7KCY26N4JDY/</a><br />\n<br />\n小六絲打寫文宣：時代揀中我哋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200416/large/1586967433_04f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200416%2Flarge%2F1586967433_04f7.jpg&h=28f9ab84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反送中運動時，S積極參與文宣工作。<br />\n<br />\n這年頭，要升讀一間好中學殊不簡單，除校內成績，面試亦同樣重要，惟小六女生S卻因疫情失去面試機會，最終不獲心儀學校取錄。<br />\n<br />\n去年的反送中運動令S一夜長大，曾贏得「最佳辯論員」獎項、成績中上的她，本打算在升中自行分配階段透過面試，獲得心儀band one中學取錄，豈料兩所目標中學因疫情取消面試，結果本月初公佈，S不獲取錄，只能等待統一派位。<br />\n<br />\n「取消咗畢業營呀，我真係好想喊呀」，升中後各散東西，S一直期待與同學參與畢業營，留下美好回憶，然而一切皆因疫情化為泡影。<br />\n<br />\n學校停課，S小學的最後時光，極可能無聲息結束，校園點滴印於腦海，「我哋小息好好玩㗎，大家追嚟追去」。話音剛落，S突然憶起一場校內小風波，「我哋隔籬班有個藍絲，之前報寸話我哋寫（文宣）嘢，成級都好憎佢」。政見不同所造成的社會撕裂，在小學生身上也可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被藍絲罵「曱甴」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：發展中國家勢受衝擊<br />\n<br />\n停課期間，S透過網上學習，為解長期留在家中的鬱悶，她閒時會彈鋼琴，或到附近公園踩滑板。曾於反送中運動積極參與文宣工作的S，長得比同齡的小六生高，看得亦比一般的11歲遠，除獨自到連儂隧道派傳單及貼文宣，亦曾在派文宣單張時被藍絲指罵為「曱甴」。<br />\n<br />\nS亦開設Instagram專頁「小學生文宣組」，她表示：「如果大家光復唔到香港嘅話，香港真係玩完。」<br />\n<br />\n經歷動盪一年，S對同屆小六畢業生有一番寄語：「我哋其實經歷咗好多嘢，唔知點解呢個時代揀咗我哋去做未來嘅主人翁，但係我哋要繼續好好咁貢獻香港。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200416/large/1586967432_ae9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200416%2Flarge%2F1586967432_ae9e.jpg&h=a061e78f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nS開設IG專頁「小學生文宣組」，現約有800人跟隨。"},{"pid":"a66769805ce8f612c3bea33f49e3e1cfbc0fac24","tid":1974744,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f324d1b525ddd376dfdd3a04a86ee0a703db3e8b","tid":1974744,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c9fa6ccd92fe871880e28720af4970a1c41c96","tid":1974744,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e615aa72e95af62404c49ea214acc0b2e988db","tid":1974744,"uid":83523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a104b8985167aadf53ea32ed47b821da1993c500","tid":1974744,"uid":52939,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"發夢見到,反攻POLY失敗個晚,真係有幾個小學高度既女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3ca2f9d068b4ad9a8619a103e2f7bb24625407","tid":1974744,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:34:27.