n冇d野係要收埋既。"},{"pid":"24335b749b510eb821a0f5cde54073b920fb12b3","tid":1974744,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333ae959b5ff00d34f2e08a65da7386de5e65398","tid":1974744,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0f603b73753ec1c682b806ce9a7dc4bb6a10d76f","tid":1974744,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"如果有咁好既思辨能力 我作為僱主又唔介意請一個無港共廢紙認證既員工呀<br />\n當然相對地，小絲打有無興趣打我d兜踎工又另一回事 或者佢能夠創立比我更好既生意都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489379d59711d188d41aeed807c47ff089deb600","tid":1974744,"uid":57815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc681ac4ecdb96bc790b7669532e388fa578b43","tid":1974744,"uid":208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"小朋友就係單純唔會分化 分化真係浪費曬任何人既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fdd63b28cbe1b01b619f4010c5e163c167bc4a","tid":1974744,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}